import React, {Component} from 'react';

import './MainNavigation.css';

import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Image from 'react-bootstrap/Image';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';

import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'

class mainNavigation extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
        <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="md" bg="dark" variant="dark">
            <Navbar.Brand href="/home">
                <Image src='./imgs/logo.png'/>
            </Navbar.Brand>
            <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
            <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
            <Nav className="mr-auto">
                <Nav.Link className="mainItem">
                    <NavLink to="/menu">Menu</NavLink>
                </Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link href="/about" className="mainItem">
                    <NavLink to="/menu">About</NavLink>
                </Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link href="/entertainment" className="mainItem">
                    <NavLink to="/menu">Entertainment</NavLink>
                </Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link href="/events" className="mainItem">
                    <NavLink to="/menu">Events</NavLink>
                </Nav.Link>
            </Nav>
            <Nav className="authBtns">
                <Nav.Link href="#deets">
                    <Button>Login</Button>
                </Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link eventKey={2} href="#memes">
                    <Button>Sign Up</Button>
                </Nav.Link>
            </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Navbar>
        )
    }
}

export default mainNavigation;
